#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.156"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.156:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.156:0.2"
msgid "16. Indriyavagga "
msgstr "16. Faculties "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: asaṅkheyyasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.156:0.3"
msgid "156. Kappasutta "
msgstr "156. Eons "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: asaṅkhyeyyāni → asaṅkheyyāni (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an4.156:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, kappassa asaṅkhyeyyāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, an eon contains four uncountable periods. "

msgctxt "an4.156:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni cattāri? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.156:1.3"
msgid "Yadā, bhikkhave, kappo saṃvaṭṭati, taṃ na sukaraṃ saṅkhātuṃ—"
msgstr "When an eon contracts, it’s not easy to calculate "

msgctxt "an4.156:1.4"
msgid "ettakāni vassānīti vā, ettakāni vassasatānīti vā, ettakāni vassasahassānīti vā, ettakāni vassasatasahassānīti vā. "
msgstr "how many years, how many hundreds or thousands or hundreds of thousands of years it takes. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.156:2.1"
msgid "Yadā, bhikkhave, kappo saṃvaṭṭo tiṭṭhati, taṃ na sukaraṃ saṅkhātuṃ—"
msgstr "When an eon remains fully contracted, it’s not easy to calculate "

msgctxt "an4.156:2.2"
msgid "ettakāni vassānīti vā, ettakāni vassasatānīti vā, ettakāni vassasahassānīti vā, ettakāni vassasatasahassānīti vā. "
msgstr "how many years, how many hundreds or thousands or hundreds of thousands of years it takes. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.156:3.1"
msgid "Yadā, bhikkhave, kappo vivaṭṭati, taṃ na sukaraṃ saṅkhātuṃ—"
msgstr "When an eon expands, it’s not easy to calculate "

msgctxt "an4.156:3.2"
msgid "ettakāni vassānīti vā, ettakāni vassasatānīti vā, ettakāni vassasahassānīti vā, ettakāni vassasatasahassānīti vā. "
msgstr "how many years, how many hundreds or thousands or hundreds of thousands of years it takes. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.156:4.1"
msgid "Yadā, bhikkhave, kappo vivaṭṭo tiṭṭhati, taṃ na sukaraṃ saṅkhātuṃ—"
msgstr "When an eon remains fully expanded, it’s not easy to calculate "

msgctxt "an4.156:4.2"
msgid "ettakāni vassānīti vā, ettakāni vassasatānīti vā, ettakāni vassasahassānīti vā, ettakāni vassasatasahassānīti vā. "
msgstr "how many years, how many hundreds or thousands or hundreds of thousands of years it takes. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.156:4.3"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, cattāri kappassa asaṅkhyeyyānī”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four uncountable periods of an eon.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.156:4.4"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
